{"tid":1255331,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"多倫多大學 specialist定double major?","createTime":"2019-06-24T12:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T18:15:34.000Z","uid":238755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ffd4af80618f39850319b71f7c88c7fcfdf90e","tid":1255331,"uid":238755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"我依加係UTSG life sciences year 1，唔知揀邊樣好 (Specialist psychology/ double major psychology + criminology)，諗住之後再係加拿大/英國/香港讀master。<br />\n<br />\nSpecialist夠專，識到多啲prof幫手寫推薦信入master，剩低可以揀bird courses。但怕深得濟會拉低GPA入唔到master/競爭力太大，同埋唔中意上seminar。<br />\n<br />\nDouble major出路廣啲，邊樣唔掂都有個拉住，同埋兩科都幾有興趣。但之後3年都完全真係讀呢啲，冇bird courses同CR，同怕master啲人見我double major而唔揀我先。<br />\n<br />\n應該揀邊個好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42e59e8c19271f514011e26698baedf26c8ebd9","tid":1255331,"uid":126503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得Specialist psychology會好D!  我讀緊child and youth care, 我都係入到去先知道children and youth 係咁嘅世界裡生活需要好有knowledge 同skills 既worker 先會有機會shine!  Double major 當然唔係唔好，但我覺得會搞到自己冇咩方向感，可能係因為我搵到自己既purpose of life 啦！希望幫到你啦！"},{"pid":"155842ea24328ed482bbcbb9cfd356bc63b274e2","tid":1255331,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"UTSG扮乜撚嘢UT？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc8d6837bd3c9f44a07b5912702481925d75545","tid":1255331,"uid":238755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155842ea24328ed482bbcbb9cfd356bc63b274e2","tid":1255331,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"UTSG扮乜撚嘢UT？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"